data.description: Mt Airy : Welcome to  this enchanting 2 Bedroom Duplex.  Thinking about a income producing property in a great neighborhood? This one is definitely for you.  Both units have been nicely remolded.  The 1st level has a nice size living room,  a pleasingly looking kitchen and bathroom both of which have been remodeled tastefully. The 2nd Level is as charming as the 1st level. The 2nd unit also has a living room, 2 bedrooms, a gracious looking kitchen and bathroom  also remolded like the 1st level.  Both units are in move-in condition there is nothing left to do except rent your moving truck. This units can provide a positive cash flow. Have you every thought about living in one unit and renting the other, one has the option of doing so. Oh not to mention this is a corner property with off street parking. A 2 car garage, now that's a plus. You won't be disappointed with this Duplex. This unit is close to schools, transportation, and shopping center. Take a drive by it, see its curb appeal you will want to see it. Owner will look at all reasonable offers.
